     <div type="preface">
   <pb facs="2"/>
   <p>
      <seg rend="decorInit">A</seg> Good / holsome lesson &amp; profytable vnto al chrystianes / ascrybed vnto saynt Bernarde / and put amonge his werkes [I thynke] by some good man / that wolde it shulde therby haue the more authoryte / and the rather be redde / and better be borne away. For doubtles it is a good mater / and edificatyue vnto all them that haue a zele / and cure vnto soule helthe &amp; desyre of saluacyon. It is called in the tytle. Notabile documētum. that is to say / a nota<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>ble lesson. And some done call it the goldē py<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>stle. It foloweth immedyately after a lytell werke called Formula honeste vite. y<seg rend="sup">e</seg> forme / and maner of an honest lyfe / or of honest ly<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>uynge.</p>
</div>
